CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 21, 1959, pg. A1 reads: "Nursery Opening - With Housing Authority Administrator Alfred L. Tronzo and Mrs. Valerie Watts, president of the sponsoring club (top left photo, third and fourth from left), women of Bedford Dwellings, known as Club 1213, opened a day nursery Monday...- Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women and men, including Alfred L. Tronzo, third from left; and Valerie Watts, fourth from left, seated at banquet table for nursery opening in Bedford Dwellings
